{{page-title "Documentation — Questions"}}
<div class="container mx-auto max-w-3xl py-6 px-4 space-y-6">

  <Panel::Card>
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-3">Questions</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600">
      Questions are application prompts you encounter during the job search —
      "Tell us about a time you led a team under pressure," or "Why are you
      interested in this role?" Career Caddy lets you capture them, attach them
      to a job post or company, and draft AI-assisted answers in context.
    </p>
    {{! <img src="" alt="screenshot of the questions list" /> }}
  </Panel::Card>

  <Panel::Card>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Where Questions Come
      From</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
      Questions can be entered at several levels:
    </p>
    <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
      <li><strong>On a Job Post</strong>
        — questions specific to that listing ("Describe a technical challenge
        you solved recently")</li>
      <li><strong>On a Job Application</strong>
        — questions from the actual application form ("Provide a writing
        sample")</li>
      <li><strong>On a Company</strong>
        — questions you know this company tends to ask (useful if you're
        applying to multiple roles)</li>
      <li><strong>Globally</strong>
        — general behavioral questions you want to have prepared answers for
        ("Tell me about yourself")</li>
    </ul>
  </Panel::Card>

  <Panel::Card>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">AI-Assisted Answers</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-3">
      From any question, you can ask the AI to draft an answer. It uses:
    </p>
    <ul class="text-gray-600 text-sm list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mb-3">
      <li>Your Career Data (background, skills, voice)</li>
      <li>The job description (if the question is linked to a job post)</li>
      <li>Any favorited answers you've previously produced</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-gray-600">
      The draft gives you a starting point. Edit it until it sounds like you,
      then mark it as a favorite to feed it back into your Career Data context.
    </p>
    {{! <img src="" alt="screenshot of a question with the AI assist button" /> }}
  </Panel::Card>

  <Panel::Card>
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-3">Example Question</h2>
    <div
      class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-200 rounded p-4 text-sm text-gray-700 space-y-2"
    >
      <div><span class="font-semibold">Question:</span>
        Tell us about a time you improved system performance. What was the
        problem, what did you do, and what was the impact?</div>
      <div><span class="font-semibold">Linked to:</span>
        Senior Full-Stack Engineer at Acme Corp</div>
      <div><span class="font-semibold">Type:</span> Behavioral / Technical</div>
      <div><span class="font-semibold">Answers:</span> 2 (1 favorited)</div>
    </div>
    {{! <img src="" alt="screenshot of a question detail page showing linked answers" /> }}
  </Panel::Card>

</div>